{"tid":1486294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察Vs示威者 & 有冇興趣考督察?","createTime":"2019-08-18T23:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T00:39:24.000Z","uid":279631,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c14eb0b9aa2018ead8278b92400895adee808d36","tid":1486294,"uid":279631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:28:00.000Z","msg":"以下問題搞下笑, 唔好咁認真。<br />\n1) 香港警察入職條件只須「在香港中學文憑考試五科考獲第2級或同等」<br />\n(即係讀書唔成可以考警察)<br />\n但係比警察毆打好多係大學生, 學歷遠高於「在香港中學文憑考試五科考獲第2級或同等」<br />\n咁, 你話合唔合理?<br />\n<br />\n2) 香港督察入職條件係「具備香港的大學學位，或同等學」<br />\n咁大學生示威者有冇興趣考入督察, 然後騎住打示威者的警察?<br />\n(如果你會的話, 你一定要保持良心, 唔好做中共抓牙, 禍害香港人)"},{"pid":"691d1b0b5b0349c0c5097db3419eddb2f4f91e43","tid":1486294,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:52:01.000Z","msg":"搞笑? 我話你老母出去勾佬生左你呢個死野仔出黎然後話搞笑阿<br />\n好唔好笑阿"},{"pid":"3a2e04836b9594339b691e45669f58481d4957a2","tid":1486294,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:53:13.000Z","msg":"2019仲講呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adb36494ef98e83fcd0beba8ebf83eb0f4e5cc9","tid":1486294,"uid":146376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:53:57.000Z","msg":"搞下笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np牌仔真係p牌仔"},{"pid":"c78699d7c3ed780152551be9ec8f860a0df3cfb7","tid":1486294,"uid":302839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:58:57.000Z","msg":"但現實上，為未來，警隊的確係需要大量換血。<br />\n如果無一批有良心，冷靜既手足入去重組，呢兩個月既事又會係未來歷史重演。"},{"pid":"9a4264548168fdce578f13e9e9d161412fef07fc","tid":1486294,"uid":300679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:39:24.000Z","msg":"重整警隊係一定<br />\n而換血最直接 <br />\n提早將老個批食肥雞餐一了百了<br />\n過渡期間，舊一批係唔係需要重新審視過佢地既道德同埋專業操守"}]}